 this story? And Old Garg says kindly, Lad (or Lass) could ya make me a Medium Banded Helm so that I may complete my Totemic Helm Quest cause that all I need Now! I got my PELT!<br><br>I went in at about 11:30PM EST and cast Sense Animals just to see if he was there.&nbsp;&nbsp;It works, if your in the area and in need of this PELT for your Totemic Helm try what I tried, maybe you too will get lucky!<br><br>Totemic Helm<br>AC 12 +5 WIS <br><br>Gargamesh Terrorbringer<br>Cazzic-Thule<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
