	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok, here's the scoop<br><br>Youu can trick the bear to automatically respawn, but it's a little tricky. how?<br><br>aggro a wandering skeleton or the lich (be careful, make sure you have sow and are out of range) and drag them near the 2 icebone teleport room.&nbsp;&nbsp;you need to be fast, but the goal is that 1) you are heading north.  then 2 you turn EAST to head down the long top east-west tunnel. whatever is chasing you will take the path of least resistance, which will be the closer tunnel (a dead end). they will get stuck here.<br><br>2) Now hurry into the broken teleporter and let it "beam" you backwards.  this will clear your aggro and, surprisingly, force a respawn of whatever was chasing you.  You need to HURRY, though, otherwise they'll catch up and start pulling on your leg.....<br><br><br><br><br>...... Just like I'm doing to you now! :)<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
