	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Sorry, the placeholder for the bear is a pair of wandering ice boned skeletons.&nbsp;&nbsp;There are other ice boned skeletons down in the caves but they are all stationary.  If you see any ice boned skeletons down there, and they happen to be walking in the tunnels or moving around, they are your placeholders.  Every time the spawn is activated, there is a 33 percent chance it could be an ice boned skeleton, the bear, or another wandering ice boned skeleton.  So, good luck and good hunting.<br><br>              Maruwindl Frostbane (Knights of Templar, E'ci)<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
	   </form></table><ul>

